{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be secure and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureGuard Cybersecurity</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #fce4ec; /* Light pink */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            background-color: rgba(229, 57, 53, 0.9); /* Slightly transparent brand color */\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: var(--light-text);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item:last-child {\n            border-bottom: none;\n        }\n\n        .service-icon {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-right: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-content h3 {\n            margin: 0 0 10px 0;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: block;\n            width: 200px;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            padding: 15px 25px;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            text-align: center;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(229, 57, 53, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #c62828; /* Darker red */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            margin-top: 40px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 70px 20px;\n            background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4), rgba(0,0,0,0.4));\n        }\n\n        .hero-section h2 {\n            color: var(--light-text);\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero-section p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>SecureGuard Cybersecurity</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero-section\">\n        <h2>Your Digital Fortress. Secured.</h2>\n        <p>Protecting your business from evolving cyber threats with cutting-edge solutions.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"services\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt service-icon\"></i>\n                <div class=\"service-content\">\n                    <h3>Threat Detection & Response</h3>\n                    <p>Proactive monitoring and rapid response to neutralize security incidents before they escalate.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-network-wired service-icon\"></i>\n                <div class=\"service-content\">\n                    <h3>Network Security</h3>\n                    <p>Fortify your network infrastructure against intrusions and unauthorized access.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-lock service-icon\"></i>\n                <div class=\"service-content\">\n                    <h3>Data Encryption</h3>\n                    <p>Ensure the confidentiality and integrity of your sensitive data with robust encryption.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-user-shield service-icon\"></i>\n                <div class=\"service-content\">\n                    <h3>Security Consulting</h3>\n                